Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: GitHub API Rate Limiting

Solution: Add authentication token to increase rate limits (5000 requests/hour)
Use time.sleep() between requests
Check rate limit status: curl -H "Authorization: token YOUR_TOKEN" https://api.github.com/rate_limit
Issue: TravisCI API Returns 404

Solution: Verify repository exists and has TravisCI enabled
Check if builds are public (private builds require authentication)
Use correct API version in headers
Issue: Secret Validation Fails

Solution: Ensure credentials are not expired or revoked
Check network connectivity to validation endpoints
Verify correct credential format (some APIs have specific requirements)
